Q-168 Implement HolyC helper `FPQ16ExpArrayCheckedNoAliasChecked` in `src/math/intexp.HC` to enforce non-aliasing (`input_q16 != output_q16`) with shared checked span math for callers that require strict source immutability during softmax staging (WS1-02)\n- [ ] IQ-169 Implement HolyC helper `FPQ16SoftmaxExpPhaseFromPreclampedChecked` in `src/math/softmax.HC` to compute exp-lanes from pre-clamped logits by composing `FPQ16ExpArrayFromClampedInputChecked` and checked sum accumulation for split-phase softmax pipelines (WS1-03)\n- [ ] IQ-170 Implement HolyC helper `FPQ16SoftmaxExpPhaseFromPreclampedNoAliasChecked` in `src/math/softmax.HC` to require disjoint input/output buffers while reusing shared checked span+sum logic for immutable-logit callers (WS1-03)\n- [ ] IQ-171 Add host-side parity harness `tests/test_softmax_exp_phase_from_preclamped_checked.py` validating pre-clamped exp-phase outputs, sum accumulation, and BAD_PARAM/NULL_PTR/no-partial-write contracts against scalar lane composition (WS1-05)\n\n\n## Progress Ledger\n\n\n| Date | Iteration | Task | Result | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| 2026-04-17 | loop-146 | IQ-167 pre-clamped exp-array helper | done | Added `FPQ16ExpArrayFromClampedInputChecked` in `src/math/intexp.HC` + `tests/test_intexp_exp_array_from_clamped_input_checked.py`; `python3 tests/test_intexp_exp_array_from_clamped_input_checked.py && python3 tests/test_intexp_exp_from_clamped_input_checked.py && python3 tests/test_intexp_clamp_array_to_input_domain_checked.py` passed |\n| 2026-04-17 | loop-145 | IQ-165 checked Q16 exp-array helper | done | Added `FPQ16ExpArrayChecked` in `src/math/intexp.HC` with checked pointer-span guards and scalar clamp+eval lane composition; `python3 - <<'PY' ... intexp_exp_array_checked_reference_checks=ok ... PY && python3 tests/test_intexp_exp_from_clamped_input_checked.py && python3 tests/test_intexp_clamp_array_to_input_domain_checked.py` passed |\n| 2026-04-17 | loop-144 | IQ-164 pre-clamped exp evaluator 